title: SARA Institute
text:
SARA Institute
Savitribai Ramabai Institute of Data Science, also called SARA Institute, is a charitable education organization. We provide free data science, research, and English language education to underrepresented students in India.
We are influenced and inspired by many Dalit, Adivasi, and Bahujan leaders for social democracy and justice. We need your love and support. Please feel free to contact us at

sara.institute.info@gmail.com
